 instrument provided the trainer feels you are capable of operating it safely and correctly else additional training is required you can discuss your experimental needsdifficulties with us during training or afterwards  at the end of training you will receive a user name and password to access the signup scheduler next training dates xrd est  jan  tuesday  –  am feb  tuesday  –  am mar  tuesday  –  am apr  tuesday  –  am    research support we gratefully acknowledge research support by nsfcbet   alstom power  doeneup  doeefrc  renewable bioproducts institute  nsfcbet   phillips   exxonmobil chemicals  dow chemical  oak ridge national laboratory  general electric  nsfcbet   arpae  algenol biofuels  nsfcareer   conocophillips  kaust  nsfeec   nsfeccs   ipst consortium  nsfstc  sandia national laboratories  georgia research alliance  exxonmobil  acsprf g  nsfcbet  nsfcbet   georgia tech startup funds                              nair research group       sankar nair research group                 at the georgia institute of technology nanoporous materials and membranes via scalable processing strategies     home current members research program our publications news facilities alumni                in the news   a selection of news items featuring the groups work over the years mof membranes chemical processing greener way to filter chemicals scientific american hollowfiber membranes sciencedaily tuning the mix science editors choice miraculous membranes delta air lines sky magazine separating ethanol from water energy at georgia tech metal oxide nanotubes eetimes nanotube formation  research horizons magazine nanotube formation sciencedaily    research group news latest only   jan  shaowei yang joins the group as a postdoctoral fellow and christine kiang as an undergraduate researcher dec  nikita kevlich awarded the ms degree oct  ya dong chiang akshay korde and byunghyun min join the group as phdtrack researchers sep  wungwi kim returns to the group as a research engineer after three years at corning fusheng pan joins the group as a visiting professor jul  vivek pisharodi awarded a pura grant for his fall  research in the nair group apr  sankar nair and christopher jones receive gt sigma xi award for best faculty paper jan  sankar nair appointed associate chair for industry outreach in chbe oct  juan hazbon and yeon hye kwon join the group as phdtrack researchers aug  emily benjamin and junyoung hwang join the group as undergraduate researchers july  tom giordano awarded a pura grant for his fall  research in the nair group june  ryan stuart joins the group as a summer ret participant from dacula high school gwinnett county    group member  alumni awards   gt chbe ziegler award for best research paper sanjoy mukherjee    gt chbe ziegler award for best research proposal dunyen kang    gt sigma xi best phd thesis award suchitra konduri    gt chbe best phd thesis award dunyen kang    gt chbe award for best performance in oral phd qualifying examination dunyen kang  jaeyub chung    gt aiche outstanding teaching assistant award dunyen kang    gt nanoscience  technology nast graduate fellow abraham greenstein    best presentation awards gt chbe graduate student symposium best poster presentation yeny hudiono nd place  best poster presentation christopher edmonds  best oral presentation christopher edmonds nd place    nd international forum on multidisciplinary education and research for energy science okinawa japan best presentation fuel cells section wungwi kim    korea research foundation fellow kwangsuk jang    doh wonsuk memorial award korean institute of chemical engineers us chapter taehyun bae    gt presidential fellow amir ahmadi    gt polymer gaann fellow amir ahmadi    gt outstanding undergraduate research award ho ming gabriel tong st place  cintia nojima nd place    aiche graduate research awards joshua thompson graduate student research award separations division    aiche undergraduate research awards veda bartlow southe